          </div>
          <span class="trust-cert">持牌认证</span>
          <span class="trust-users">12万+ 活跃玩家</span>
        </div>
        <div class="zone s-payment">
          <span class="zone-label lbl-shared">共用</span>
          <div class="pay-title">支付方式</div>
          <div class="pay-logos">
            <div class="pay-logo pl-oxxo">OXXO</div>
            <div class="pay-logo pl-clabe">CLABE</div>
            <div class="pay-logo pl-pc">PayCash</div>
            <div class="pay-logo pl-bank">银行卡</div>
          </div>
          <div class="pay-promise">
            <div class="check"></div>
            无条件提款 · 3分钟到账
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="zone s-benefits">
          <span class="zone-label lbl-fixed">固定</span>
          <div class="benefit-item"><span class="benefit-num">1.</span><span class="benefit-text">注册即领 <span>$80</span> 彩金，无需充值</span></div>
          <div class="benefit-item"><span class="benefit-num">2.</span><span class="benefit-text">首充翻倍 <span>+100%</span>，额外奖励</span></div>
          <div class="benefit-item"><span class="benefit-num">3.</span><span class="benefit-text">每日登录奖励最高 <span>999,999</span></span></div>
          <div class="benefit-item"><span class="benefit-num">4.</span><span class="benefit-text">提款 <span>无条件</span>，随存随取</span></div>
          <div class="benefit-item"><span class="benefit-num">5.</span><span class="benefit-text">千款游戏，<span>100%</span> 返还率</span></div>
          <div class="benefit-item"><span class="benefit-num">6.</span><span class="benefit-text">邀友奖励最高 <span>1,000,000</span></span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="zone s-games">
          <span class="zone-label lbl-fixed">固定</span>
          <div class="game-cat-title">老虎机</div>
          <div class="game-row">
            <div class="game-thumb"><div class="game-hot">热</div></div>
            <div class="game-thumb"></div><div class="game-thumb"></div><div class="game-thumb"></div><div class="game-thumb"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="game-cat-title">真人娱乐场</div>
          <div class="game-row">
            <div class="game-thumb"><div class="game-hot">新</div></div>
            <div class="game-thumb"></div><div class="game-thumb"></div><div class="game-thumb"></div><div class="game-thumb"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="game-cat-title">体育</div>
          <div class="game-row">
            <div class="game-thumb"></div><div class="game-thumb"></div><div class="game-thumb"></div><div class="game-thumb"></div><div class="game-thumb"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="zone s-cs">
          <span class="zone-label lbl-shared">共用</span>
          <div class="cs-text"><strong>需要帮助？</strong>24小时在线客服</div>
          <div class="cs-wa">WhatsApp</div>
        </div>
        <div class="zone s-sticky">
          <span class="zone-label lbl-shared">共用</span>
